pibootctl (0.5-0ubuntu1) groovy; urgency=medium

  * Configuration re-writing always targets config.txt
  * Added comment_lines option to permit commenting lines instead of
    deleting them
  * Configuration writer searches for an uncomments lines in preference to
    writing new ones
  * Added --this-model and --this-serial options to permit adding settings
    to new/existing conditional sections

 -- Dave Jones <dave.jones@canonical.com>  Wed, 09 Sep 2020 00:10:31 +0100

